  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Residential vs commercial trash compactor — disambiguation</h2>
    <p>Jenn-Air residential trash compactor (JCR 15-inch, 1.4 cubic foot chamber, household-scale daily-bag compaction in a built-in kitchen) is a different product category from commercial trash chute compactors (10+ cubic yard capacity, apartment-building or multi-unit residential chute-fed installations) and commercial industrial waste balers (manufacturing + distribution-center scrap + recycling scale). Jenn-Air does NOT manufacture commercial-scale trash compactors — the brand is residential only. Our SDAR service scope is residential-only; we do not service commercial trash chute compactors or industrial waste balers. If your situation is commercial scale (multi-unit apartment building trash chute compactor, industrial waste baler, high-volume commercial-kitchen compactor), please search for commercial-specialist service rather than a residential appliance-repair company.</p>
    <p>Jenn-Air's parent company Whirlpool Corporation similarly focuses on residential appliances — no commercial-scale trash compactor product exists under the Jenn-Air or Whirlpool brand umbrella. When you see a commercial trash compactor in an LA apartment building or commercial property, that's typically a Marathon, Wastequip, or similar commercial-waste-management manufacturer — entirely separate industry from residential appliance brands.</p>
